              "fill": "$ink",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Oonchiumpa, a 100% Aboriginal-owned consultancy in Alice Springs, leads the design and the build. Palm Island Community Company partners on delivery. The advisory group includes Aboriginal leaders, the managing director of Zinus, one of Australia’s largest bedding makers, and our industrial-design partner Defy. Two founders run it today, with a general manager and a business lead next to hire.",
