          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 1500,
          "content": "Goods is one of ten enterprises selected for Catalysing Impact, powered by Social Impact Hub in partnership with the QBE Foundation. QBE will contribute up to $400,000 of untied funding, on one condition: that other funders commit matched capital first. So an early commitment is not only support. It is the thing that brings the rest of the raise, and the QBE contribution behind it.",
